# Reference for wand types from GemStone IV Wiki.
# Source: https://gswiki.play.net/Wand#List_of_wands
# Author: Starsworn (with assistance from Claude AI)
#
# C = Crumbly (destroyed when charges depleted)
# T = Can be found as treasure
# A = Can be crafted with alchemy
#
# Usage:
#   ;wands             - display full wand table
#   ;wands <name>      - display detail for a specific wand (partial name match)
#   ;wands help        - show usage

